description: Vocalist, guitarist, and jazz icon George Benson joins Christian McBride for a conversation about his early years on the jazz scene, fame and his new “lost” album.
title: George Benson on success, critics and staying true to himself

description: Rumaan Alam’s previous novel was an inspired swirl of suspense, social commentary and apocalyptic disaster. His latest is about a young Black woman working for a uber-rich white socialite.
title: 'Entitlement' disappoints — 'Leave the World Behind' was a tough act to follow

description: Gustavo and Otavio Pandolfo are best known as the artist duo Osgemeos. They've been making art in tandem since they were kids in São Paulo, Brazil.
title: 'We are like one artist': These identical twins are in sync from graffiti to gallery

description: As they fought to keep Sean "Diddy" Combs out of jail after his sex trafficking arrest, the music mogul's lawyers highlighted a litany of horrors at the Brooklyn federal lockup where he was headed.
title: Inside the Brooklyn jail where Sean Combs is locked up: violence, squalor and death
